                Grumsh Has a notorious hatred of the other gods. Some say this hatred stems from there refusal to accept him as a god, others say it is there refusal to accept Orcs as civlized, regardless Grumsh was forced to carve out land for the orcs to live creating the badlands
                and punched holes in mountains to create caves to shelter his people. Grumsh teaches his followers to 
                take land and pillage what they can find, to survive even in the world that wants nothing to do with them, BUT only take what is nessecary, books, gold, and magic tomes are rarely taken, although somtimes they can be eaten.
                <br>
                Grumsh is responsible for the domains of war, chaos and survival
                <br>
                His holy symbol is a red eye with a black pupil.
          
              </p>
